Feature: BookStore
  Scenario: Sending Api requests and verifying results of the requests
    * Send a post request to create a user in bookstore
    * Send a post request to generate a token
    * Authorize user created with token generated
    * Send a get request to get a book list from the system
    * Get the books published by No Starch Press from the list
    * Send a post request to add selected books to user account
    * Send a get request to get the user by Id

